# What is the primary purpose of President Zelensky's visit to the United States?

## Summary
Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky is making his first trip outside Ukraine since it was invaded 300 days ago to visit Washington, DC and rally his top international partner behind sustained military and economic assistance. He will meet with US President Joe Biden in the Oval Office and address a joint meeting of Congress on Capitol Hill in the evening. Biden will announce he is sending nearly $2 billion in additional security assistance to Ukraine, including a sophisticated new air defense system. His visit is intended to thank Congress and the American people for their support and to ask for additional help in defending Ukraine from Russian invasion. <font color=#FF3399>[1,2,3,5]</font>

